    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Smaller version of any bag in fashion, usually beaded, sequinned, or embroidered, or of some glamorous fabric such as kid, silver, bronze, or gold.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
